3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with time-lapse image sequences. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper uses regularization terms to detect moving objects and illumination changes, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper uses a novel method to address the weaknesses of existing methods, which can be seen as an application of artificial intelligence.
